ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Tile
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
local buttons = {}

local button_value = {}
button_value.index = 0
button_value.click_function = 'doNothing'
button_value.function_owner = self
button_value.label = tostring(value)
button_value.position = {0,0.2,-0.23}
button_value.width = 1000
button_value.height = 600
button_value.font_size = 550
table.insert(buttons, button_value)

local button_minus = {}
button_minus.index = 1

button_minus.click_function = 'minus'
button_minus.function_owner = self

button_minus.label = '-'
button_minus.position = {-1.2,0.2,0.7}
button_minus.width = 250
button_minus.height = 250
button_minus.font_size = 250
button_minus.color = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5}
button_minus.font_color= {1, 1, 1}
table.insert(buttons, button_minus)

local button_plus = {}
button_plus.index = 2

button_plus.click_function = 'plus'
button_plus.function_owner = self

button_plus.label = '+'
button_plus.position = {1.2,0.2,0.7}
button_plus.width = 250
button_plus.height = 250
button_plus.font_size = 250
button_plus.color = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5}
button_plus.font_color= {1, 1, 1}
table.insert(buttons, button_plus)

local button_reset = {}
button_reset.index = 3

button_reset.click_function = 'reset'
button_reset.function_owner = self

button_reset.label = 'Reset'
button_reset.position = {0,0.2,0.8}
button_reset.width = 400
button_reset.height = 200
button_reset.font_size = 120
button_reset.color = {0.5, 0.5, 0.5}
button_reset.font_color= {1, 1, 1}
table.insert(buttons, button_reset)

function onSave()
    local data_to_save = {value=value}
    local saved_data = JSON.encode(data_to_save)
    return saved_data
end

function onload(saved_data)

    if saved_data ~= nil and saved_data ~= "" then
        local loaded_data = JSON.decode(saved_data)
        value = loaded_data.value
    else
        value = 0

    end

    for _, button in ipairs(buttons) do
        self.createButton(button)
    end
    button_value.label = tostring(value)
    self.editButton(button_value)
end


-- functions
function doNothing()
end

function updatevalue()
    if value < 0 then
        value = 0
    end 
    button_value.label = tostring(value)
    self.editButton(button_value)
    self.setVar("blueBonusLevel", value)
end

function reset(clicked_object, clicker)
    value = 0
    button_value.label = tostring(value)
    self.editButton(button_value)
    self.setVar("blueBonusLevel", value)
end

function minus(clicked_object, clicker)
    value = value-1
    updatevalue()
end

function plus(clicked_object, clicker)
    value = value+1
    updatevalue()
end
